lead_paragraph: Hull City manager Mike Phelan has praised his team for their resilience after they beat second-tier Newcastle United in the League Cup to reach the semi-finals.

headline.print_headline: Newcastle Win Was a Result Hull Deserved, Says Phelan
headline.main: Newcastle Win Was a Result Hull Deserved, Says Phelan
